uh this this goes back to this business of free speech you know where there was a time a couple of years back uh two or three years back maybe you know where i think i've mentioned this where they had the right to insult well nobody has a right to insult anybody it was a very harsh way of expressing the fact that you can be assertive about your opinion about your perspective

